PrecisAuthorization for the leasing by the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to the CORPORATION OF THE CITY OF NEPEAN, for a term of 15 years, of the NATIONAL CAPITAL EQUESTRIAN PARK property situated at 401 Corkstown Road, Nepean, comprising 110 hectares of land, for use as a public facility for recreation, training and competition in equestrian sports.
